# Blocks and Interactivity (Query Filter)

- Source lives in `src/<block>/`; register in `index.js` from `block.json`. Run **`npm run build`** after changes.
- **filter-container** is the parent of checkbox/search/sort/reset; provides `query-filter/queryId` context.
- View scripts use `@wordpress/interactivity` store id **`query-filter`**. Align client payloads with **`QLIF_Request`** (e.g. structured `filters`, `filtersRelationship`).
- DOM selectors for filter UI blocks must match generated classes: **`.wp-block-query-filter-filter-checkboxes`**, **`.wp-block-query-filter-filter-sort`** (derived from block names with `filter-` infix).
- URL sync: use short keys **`search`**, **`pg`**, **`frel`**; do not reintroduce a `qf_` prefix for new params.
